room_title: Escape room "Shanghaied" by Escapology Fort Lauderdale in Miami
room_address: 17 S Fort Lauderdale Beach Blvd #300 Fort Lauderdale, FL 33316
room_description: Trapped on a ship together with your friends, you have lost all hope for regaining freedom. However, today, if you dare, you can try to uncover the hidden map and find your way out of here! If you get caught, you're walking the plank. So don't get caught... Do you have what it takes to escape the clutches of Captain Kellett?
